name: Elena Ivanova
summary: Elena Ivanova is a 35 year old woman and healthcare professional from Moscow, Russia, currently residing in Los Angeles, California. Professionally, she serves as a Physician and appreciates the virtues of education, honesty, and adventure. Elena holds a doctoral degree and identifies as agnostic and liberal in her religious and political affiliations. She is seeking a life partner and is open to starting a family in the future as she doesn't have any children but desires to have some. Her interests are diverse and include cooking, reading, music, and hiking. A lover of cats, Elena exercises religiously, doesn't smoke, and indulges in drinks occasionally. As a Virgo and an INFJ, Elena is looking for a straight man between the ages of 33-45 who is also active, a non-smoker, open to having children, and shares her love for cats.
